# .trivyignore
#
# CVE allowlist for the matchup-thumbs image.
#
# Policy (D-05): Only fixable HIGH/CRITICAL CVEs may be added here,
# and only when a remediation path is not yet available. Unfixable/
# will_not_fix findings are automatically suppressed by the Trivy
# workflow step via `ignore-unfixed: true` and do not need to be
# listed here.
#
# A CVE listed here is accepted-but-not-blocking; document the reason
# inline. Remove entries once an upstream fix is available.
#
# Local scan performed: 2026-06-14
# Command: trivy image --severity HIGH,CRITICAL --ignore-unfixed sports-media-gen-api:latest
# Result: CLEAN — zero fixable HIGH/CRITICAL CVEs found in debian:12.14 base
# or any Python package in the venv. No CVE lines needed at this time.
#
# Rebuild and rescan periodically (every 30 days or before each release).
